I'm honestly probably driving my family crazy with how often and loudly I'm playing both the most recent albums and all the old vlogs. But watching you two in your vlogs and especially the hope you brought with the Together video, makes things a little easier! You guys remind me of my two younger brothers 😁 Thank you from the bottom of my heart! Good bless you all and your families!! Stay safe and healthy!!
